body:
###...tell it where your font file(s) are located and let it take care of the rest!

This module is not tightly coupled to any specific font libraries or apis. It also is not opinionated about how you get the fonts on your machine. installfont is currently scoped to windows operating system. You can find a mac solution here: FTPM

Open your command line and run `npm install installfont`

Fast start
```javascript
var installfont = require('installfont');

installfont('path/to/your/font.ttf', function(err) {
  if(err) console.log(err, err.stack);;
  //handle callback tasks here
});
```
